    "Innovative methods such as RA-ISF (retrieval-augmented iterative self-feedback) decompose tasks into submodules, enhancing factual reasoning and reducing hallucinations (Liu et al. 2024).",
    "These examples are intended to reflect the potential that RAG has to offer.",
